name: Disco Sufi
description:
If we are going to know that there is more than one character in every being, I think we should do something in order to be transparent, to bring out what is hidden inside us, our other characters that we are afraid to show to others. Every self and character is just a reflection of what we see. Other personas lurk deep inside.

Introducing 'Disco Sufi' in the 90's
Dimension: 2048x2020px
